channel.title: JRAT found back-door java.(Don't know where to post)
channel.description:
My pc has caught a JRAT about an hour ago by downloading one of the "clients" on the server status page. I'm not familiar with these kind of things, but it seems to be a java back-door application which can break into your computer. I suggest this server to be removed from the serverstatus page.
http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=InfinityPk.no-ip.biz
^ That is the link with the JRAT.
Please correct me when I'm wrong. I appreciate your comments and I want to learn of them.
